f=Brand Studio/pixel/marketplace/content-image/SKILL.md · tx=<!-- Unmodified copy "content-image" (vstorm-co/content-skills), fulfilling catalog's prompt-engineering-visual slot ("structure: subject-style-light-lens; iterate weakest axis; upscale pipeline" skill's four-component structure, variations discipline, model-specific optimization). NOTES SYSTEM: "brand/VISUAL.md" reads map atlas's brand kit pixel's image-style-guide file brand-alignment section exactly seam image-style-guide's constants plug in. honest "generates prompts, images" framing matches our deployment reality: generation connector exists, asset-pipeline executes prompts; doesn't, prompts themselves deliverable. Redirects content-infographic/content-presentation source-repo pointers, local skills. --> · h2:Important: Skill Generates Prompts, Images=Claude cannot generate images. skill produces **ready-to-paste prompts** optimized image generation models. output text user copies DALL-E, Midjourney, Stable Diffusion, another image generation tool. output includes: prompt text (optimized target model) Recommended model settings Negative prompt (where model supports it) Variations try · h2:Prompt Structure=effective image prompt four components: · h3:1. Subject=What image. specific concrete. · h3:1. Subject=Bad: "a person working", Good: software developer sitting standing desk dual monitors, writing code, coffee mug nearby" · h3:1. Subject=subject described enough detail two different artists produce recognizably similar images. · h3:2. Style=visual treatment. Reference specific style style library describe explicitly. · h3:2. Style=Bad: "nice looking", Good: "editorial photography, shallow depth field, natural window light, 35mm lens" · h3:2. Style=See `style-library/` pre-built style descriptions: · h3:2. Style=`style-library/editorial.md` Clean, professional photography, `style-library/flat-illustration.md` Bold, geometric, vector-like, `style-library/3d-render.md` Soft lighting, smooth surfaces, product-shot feel, `style-library/film-still.md` Cinematic, dramatic, atmospheric · h3:3. Mood / Atmosphere=emotional tone image. · h3:3. Mood / Atmosphere=Calm, focused, productive, Energetic, vibrant, optimistic, Dramatic, tense, high-stakes, Warm, inviting, approachable, Minimal, quiet, contemplative · h3:4. Technical Specs=Resolution, aspect ratio, model-specific parameters. · h3:4. Technical Specs=Aspect ratio: 16:9 (hero banners), 1:1 (social), 4:5 (Instagram portrait), 3:2 (blog photos), Quality: high detail, photorealistic vs. stylized, Lighting: natural, studio, dramatic, flat, backlighting, Camera: wide angle, close-up, overhead, eye-level · h2:Brand Alignment=generating prompts, align brand aesthetic `brand/VISUAL.md`: · h3:Color Alignment=brand uses warm earth tones, suggest prompts with: · h3:Color Alignment="warm lighting, golden hour, earth tones, amber terracotta palette" · h3:Color Alignment=brand uses cool blues grays, suggest: · h3:Color Alignment="cool lighting, blue-gray tones, steel slate palette, overcast sky" · h3:Color Alignment=force brand colors image, guide aesthetic direction. · h3:Style Alignment=\| Brand Aesthetic \| Prompt Direction \| · h3:Style Alignment=\|---\|---\| · h3:Style Alignment=\| Minimal, clean \| "clean composition, negative space, simple background, uncluttered" \| · h3:Style Alignment=\| Bold, vibrant \| "saturated colors, dynamic composition, high contrast, energetic" \| · h3:Style Alignment=\| Corporate, professional \| "studio lighting, neutral background, polished, sharp focus" \| · h3:Style Alignment=\| Playful, creative \| "whimsical elements, bright colors, unexpected angles, hand-drawn feel" \| · h3:Style Alignment=\| Technical, precise \| "technical illustration, blueprint aesthetic, grid lines, precise geometry" \| · h3:Consistency Across Assets=generating multiple prompts project (e.g., series blog post images), maintain consistency: · h3:Consistency Across Assets=style mood across prompts, aspect ratio quali